name: Trebuchet (itch) (Lady Dana)
description:
(the 'O' button is Z on the keyboard)

Catch the enemy's boulder, but don't let your trebuchet get hit! use the left and right arrow keys to move but watch out for the flags that limit how far you can go.

Made for the Mini Jame Gam 2023. The first game ever finished by Dana St. Amand
